title: American Horror Stories Episode 5 Ba’al Synopsis and Review
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: Matt and Ivy would really be best friends. Honestly that twist is the Scarier than any supernatural elements, the fact that someone could do that to their spouse. This was truly billie’s best performance yet! I know she is gonna play the hell out of Lark Double Feature
FINALLY! An adult episode.  And excellent episode.  Little shallow it was all a plot, and everyone was in on it...but The best episode yet!
I would really like more dark, serious episodes like this. Pleasant surprise after the cheese of the last one.

This episode was brilliant! A twist I did not see coming but expected. Billie’s character had an excellent build up. And when she goes to the prison in that bad ass outfit!!!!!!!!!!!!!! 9/10 stars loved every second
This episode was basically an AHS Cult summary, with a hint of coven crossover. Loved it
